text: Emmerson Houghton (born 7 August 1999) is a New Zealand water polo player. She competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2016 FINA World Women's Youth Water Polo Championships, 2017 Vodafone Cup, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
